From Alice Sanders Subject Re Antihistamine for sleep aid But after you have taken antihistamines for a few nights doesn't it start to have a paradoxical effect I used to take one every night for allergies and couldn't figure out why I developed bad Finally figured out it was the I would fall asleep for a few minutes but would awaken at the drop of a pin a little later and could not get back to I don't have that problem since I stopped the antihistamines at Alice